[ ] asan
[ ] log groups for debugging
[ ] BFD font letter misalignment
[ ] inconsistent type usage cleanup

== ideas ==
- haskell-like curried language on top of prolog, real-time effect inference while typing
- runtime dynamic linker (resolve calls at load time, avoid full syscall ABI)
